### 1) (선택) 로그인해서 토큰 발급 받기 — 응답 body/헤더에서 accessToken 복사
# POST http://192.168.0.160:8000/member/login
# Content-Type: application/json
#
# {
#   "memberId": "master",
#   "password": "비밀번호"
# }

### 2) /whoami 호출 — 위에서 복사한 JWT를 아래에 붙여넣으세요
GET http://192.168.0.160:8000/whoami
Authorization: Bearer {{eyJhbGciOiJIUzM4NCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiJtYXN0ZXIiLCJpYXQiOjE3NjA0NDk3ODAsImV4cCI6MTc2MDQ1MDY4MH0.W-wX8R8iTO8Fj-or9Zl6HdfveJRjfAv7IMVwcImuUnYZAWFDpQ0JVDRYiBx_6ZjL}}
